name: ExampleMyShoes
title: Example My Shoes
description: The Example My Shoes Logical Model Mindmap is shown below.

element.definition:
**My shoe record**
 Covers the core aspects of shoe ownership.
  - Preferred types
  - Appropriate sizes
  - A shoe by shoe record including:
    - Approval by experts
	- Details of sizing
	 - Brand etc.

**Style of Shoe**
For example
* Sandals /Jandals
* Sneakers
* Slip-ons
* Boat Shoes
* Stillettos
* Platforms

National Individual Shoe Identifier (ISI)
The HI Service can validate an ISI using information:
- Colour
- Brand
- Serial Number
- Other
